          "type": "rtf",
          "settings": {
            "richtext_content": "<p>Ross’s journey is a testament to what happens when you combine extreme physical endurance with mental resilience. From setting records to inspiring millions, he continues to break down barriers and inspire people to redefine what they think is possible.</p><p>Founded on mindset, discipline, resilience and gratitude, the Stoic Collection celebrates the stoic mindset shared by Gym King and Ross Edgley.</p>"
